That's what you always said.

371
00:13:44,414 --> 00:13:45,331
Don't listen to me.

372
00:13:45,415 --> 00:13:46,916
Oh, so smooth.

373
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:49,085
It's like a baby's bottom. [INHALES]

374
00:13:49,169 --> 00:13:50,503
And so fragrant.

375
00:13:50,587 --> 00:13:52,421
Okay, okay.

376
00:13:52,505 --> 00:13:54,255
Tell me why you're here.

377
00:13:54,339 --> 00:13:56,174
The comic I told you about,
the one I'm representing.

378
00:13:56,258 --> 00:13:57,926
-The girl?
-Yeah, the girl.

379
00:13:58,010 --> 00:14:00,345
She's been killing at the
Gaslight, night after night.

380
00:14:00,429 --> 00:14:01,346
What's her name again?

381
00:14:01,430 --> 00:14:02,847
It's Amanda Gleason.

382
00:14:02,931 --> 00:14:03,973
Shit name.

383
00:14:04,057 --> 00:14:05,809
Fake name but a great comic.

384
00:14:05,893 --> 00:14:08,144
She'd be the perfect
opening act for Sophie Lennon.

385
00:14:08,228 --> 00:14:10,825
Get out of here.
Sophie's one of my biggest clients.

386
00:14:10,909 --> 00:14:11,314
I know.

387
00:14:11,398 --> 00:14:13,566
Where do you come off,
asking for something like this?

388
00:14:13,650 --> 00:14:15,864
I'm not talking about
opening for her at the Copa.

389
00:14:15,948 --> 00:14:16,444
Then what?

390
00:14:16,528 --> 00:14:17,946
Sophie plays those joints in Jersey

391
00:14:18,030 --> 00:14:19,280
when she's working up a new act.

392
00:14:19,364 --> 00:14:21,116
Those little dives, unannounced.

393
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,951
Let my girl open for her there.

394
00:14:23,035 --> 00:14:24,201
-Really?
-Yeah.

395
00:14:24,285 --> 00:14:25,536
That's a shit gig.

396
00:14:25,620 --> 00:14:26,954
It's a terrible gig.

397
00:14:27,038 --> 00:14:28,497
The audience is there for Sophie.

398
00:14:28,581 --> 00:14:30,833
-The opener gets eaten alive.
-We're game.

399
00:14:30,917 --> 00:14:33,085
Slot went to Markie Diamond once.
You hear of him?

400
00:14:33,169 --> 00:14:34,670
-No.
-And to Adam Young once.

401
00:14:34,754 --> 00:14:35,963
-You hear of him?
-No.

402
00:14:36,047 --> 00:14:37,381
Danny LeMonde? Scoop LeMonde?

403
00:14:37,465 --> 00:14:39,091
-Brothers?
-They're in plumbing now.

404
00:14:39,175 --> 00:14:41,760
-I get the point.
-She'd be a sacrificial lamb.

405
00:14:41,844 --> 00:14:44,513
Then cut her up into chops
and serve her with mint sauce.

406
00:14:44,597 --> 00:14:45,764
I want this for her.

407
00:14:45,848 --> 00:14:47,516
I'd need to see her first.

408
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,934
She's got a tight ten.

409
00:14:49,018 --> 00:14:50,644
I can set you up any night you like.

410
00:14:50,728 --> 00:14:52,646
-I'm not going to the Gaslight.
-Why not?

411
00:14:52,730 --> 00:14:54,064
I don't go downtown anymore.

412
00:14:54,148 --> 00:14:56,065
You cut your teeth
haunting dives downtown.

413
00:14:56,149 --> 00:14:57,316
I got nice suits now.

414
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,943
Why you wearing this one?

415
00:14:59,027 --> 00:15:01,404
The Stork Club is as
south as I want to go.

416
00:15:01,488 --> 00:15:02,655
She'll perform anywhere you want,

417
00:15:02,739 --> 00:15:04,365
but the Gaslight's her home.

418
00:15:04,449 --> 00:15:05,950
[SIGHS]

419
00:15:06,034 --> 00:15:08,077
It's a really shit gig.

420
00:15:08,161 --> 00:15:09,078
[CHUCKLES SOFTLY]

421
00:15:09,162 --> 00:15:10,496
She's gonna bomb.

422
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:11,664
[APPLAUSE]

423
00:15:11,748 --> 00:15:14,125
SOPHIE: Put that on your plate!

424
00:15:14,209 --> 00:15:18,379
Yeah, I'm from Queens, born and raised.

425
00:15:18,463 --> 00:15:21,215
Queens is the place
you go to get to the airport

426
00:15:21,299 --> 00:15:23,593
