-[LAUGHTER]

427
00:15:23,677 --> 00:15:26,429
[LAUGHS] Put that on your plate. Ugh.

428
00:15:26,513 --> 00:15:29,264
In Queens, we got a
neighborhood called Flushing,

429
00:15:29,348 --> 00:15:31,933
which isn't a name so
much as a suggestion

430
00:15:32,017 --> 00:15:34,019
for what to do with the place.

431
00:15:34,103 --> 00:15:37,564
-[LAUGHTER]
-Put that on your plate!

432
00:15:37,648 --> 00:15:40,567
