started poking me with a stick,

460
00:16:44,963 --> 00:16:46,714
looking for my blowhole!

461
00:16:46,798 --> 00:16:47,966
[LAUGHTER]

462
00:16:48,050 --> 00:16:50,051
I walked by a construction site,

463
00:16:50,135 --> 00:16:53,137
and the workers start
whistling at each other!

464
00:16:53,221 --> 00:16:54,472
[LAUGHTER]

465
00:16:54,556 --> 00:16:56,391
Should I talk about my husbands?

466
00:16:56,475 --> 00:16:58,101
[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]

467
00:16:58,185 --> 00:17:00,353
All right then. You asked for it.

468
00:17:00,437 --> 00:17:03,689
