472
00:17:11,530 --> 00:17:12,698
Bop!

473
00:17:12,782 --> 00:17:13,949
[LAUGHTER]

474
00:17:14,033 --> 00:17:16,410
[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]

475
00:17:17,870 --> 00:17:21,457
Oh! Put that on your plate!

476
00:17:26,212 --> 00:17:28,130
SOPHIE: Here you go.

477
00:17:28,214 --> 00:17:29,882
[CHUCKLES] What's your name, sweetie?

478
00:17:29,966 --> 00:17:31,383
Linda. I'm from Queens, too.

479
00:17:31,467 --> 00:17:34,218
Oh, Linda, you have
my deepest sympathies.

480
00:17:34,302 --> 00:17:36,053
-[CHUCKLES]
